&gt; On Tue, Feb 10, 2026 at 7:03 AM Philip Jägenstedt &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="7b1d14145555553b1813091416120e165514091c"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; 
