&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://github.com/web-platform-dx/developer-signals/issues/170#issuecomment-3894089666"&gt;https://github.com/web-platform-dx/developer-signals/issues/170#issuecomment-3894089666&lt;/a&gt;

