&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt; On Fri, Jul 31, 2020, 18:10 Yoav Weiss &lt;&lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="fa8395d4d4d4ba83959b8cd48d89"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
