&gt;&gt; &lt;a href="/cdn-cgi/l/email-protection" class="__cf_email__" data-cfemail="c0b9afa1b6b7a5eeeeee80a3a8b2afada9b5adeeafb2a7"&gt;[email&#160;protected]&lt;/a&gt;&gt; wrote:
