&lt;pre&gt;I've updated the CSS gradient tests for this here:
&lt;a  rel="nofollow" href="https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/7077316"&gt;https://chromium-review.googlesource.com/c/chromium/src/+/7077316&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;pre&gt;

There are also canvas gradient WPT tests (which is a feature that hasn't
made it into the spec yet). I've updated the tests and our (speculative)
implementation to include display-p3-linear.


